        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2374884142" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer317034569649241534">This was a good addition to the series and there was a lot of action but for some reason I expected more with a book with both the weasel and wolf in one book. Ending got crazy though and really added action to the story. The ending brought it from 3.5* to ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️. Still loving this series. On to Mary, Mary now. <br/><br/>My quick and simple overall: quick and entertaining afternoon read. <br/><br/>🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺🐺</span>

          </span>
