        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2765527119" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15086858586759865266">Ugh, always a like-hate relationship with Patterson’s books. This one not much to like- juvenile writing, cartoonish characters, and over the top implausible plot. So am I going to continue reading the series? Yeah, probably the next one will be better. But this wasn’t it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


